data.description: This charming home is priced below market value due to cosmetic repairs needed, offering an incredible opportunity to build equity fast. 3 Bedrooms, 1 bathroom home, with large living room and laundry room.  Whether you're an investor seeking a profitable project or a homeowner eager to customize your dream space, this property is ideal for you! The roof and carpets are 3 years old!  All brick home with a huge fenced lot.  Act now and turn this diamond in the rough into your perfect home sweet home!
